net.casper.data.model

Class CMarkedUpRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.casper.data.model.CMarkedUpRow

  • public class CMarkedUpRow
extends Object
    Represents a single CDataRow with its CRowMetaData. Provides accessors for getting row data via column name and index.
    Version:
    $Revision: 125 $
    Author:
    Oliver Mannion
